1.1 Version 4.0.7
─────────────────

1.1.1 Improve helm-dwim-target-directory
╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌

  You can use now M-n to cycle in default directories bound to each
  window.


1.1.2 Add tldr action to helm-man
╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌

  See <https://github.com/tealdeer-rs/tealdeer> and
  <https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr> Don't forget to feed the cache if
  not already done:

  tldr –update


1.1.3 file-name-history in HFF is now inconditionally using recentf
╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌

  The user vars `helm-ff-file-name-history-use-recentf` and
  `helm-files-save-history-extra-sources` have been removed.


1.1.4 Improve splitting helm-window
╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌

  We can now split in both directions with two different commands (C-r
  and C-t).


1.1.5 helm-packages is now showing new packages
╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌╌


